n-verbal elements in discourse in general and humor in particular as co-speech gestures are essential for the understanding of the message as intended by the speakers.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aHumor. 4aMimik. 4aMultimodalität. 4aSarkasmus. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aFacial Expressions.  aHumor.  aMultimodality.  aSarcasm.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2019 Part 1z978311076246408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton Contemporary 2016-2019z978311074297808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019 Englishz978311061030708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019z9783110606287oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831106259810 cprintz978311062589940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311062944640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110629446423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110629446/original  a978-3-11-061030-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-074297-8  De Gruyter Mouton Contemporary 2016-2019c2016d2019  a978-3-11-076246-4  DG Plus DeG Package 2019 Part 1b2019  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-al